Package: srametadata
Title: Getting and cleaning metadata from Sequence Read Archive (SRA)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jose", "Alquicira Hernandez", email = "joseah@lcg.unam.mx", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is designed to get, manipulate and normalize metadata from SRA easily. 
    A manifest file is generated for each run.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0), RSQLite, magrittr, stringr, SRAdb
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr, BiocStyle
